WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.440
when I was learning and started making videos.

00:00:02.440 --> 00:00:06.420
What I ended up doing is I went from beginner

00:00:06.420 --> 00:00:08.800
all the way to as advanced as I felt I could get.

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:10.200
And then I would go back and be like,

00:00:10.200 --> 00:00:13.780
okay, this beginning stuff was really tough

00:00:13.780 --> 00:00:15.000
because I didn't understand this.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:16.400
So I need to make these connections.

00:00:16.400 --> 00:00:19.600
So I would write out like almost like a diagram

00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:24.600
of here's how I got to that end project or that end result.

00:00:24.780 --> 00:00:28.240
And let me write out like the steps that I need to

00:00:28.240 --> 00:00:30.760
in order to teach it so that they understand

00:00:30.760 --> 00:00:31.959
that this is connected to this,

00:00:31.959 --> 00:00:34.240
even though they don't really know that yet.

00:00:35.080 --> 00:00:38.080
In a really beginner level friendly way

00:00:38.080 --> 00:00:41.119
that I wish the person who I was learning from had done it.

